  "title": "华为放出「准万亿级 MoE 推理」大招，两大杀手级优化技术直接开源",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651004732&idx=1&sn=a2d0e89848e7c6c802b2536eaa650863",
  "date": "2025-11-28 04:08:00",
